So, in one level (level 12), from the ding 12 to the ding 13, without any death, and allways both getting the XP  for each kills (I mean we were everytime both close enough from the mobs when they died to get the XP), and she (the warrior) ended up with more than one blue bub XP than me(cleric) (she dinged 13 when I still had a bit more than one blue to go). Any explainations ?<br>
Anyone got any informations about how XP are working or something ?<br>
Thanks<br>
